description:
Koi stray dogs se darta hain, koi unke liye ladta hai. Koi dogs ko khaana deta hai, aur koi kehta hai kutte bhi khaa lo!

Phir bhi, aam aadmi kutton ko pasand na bhi karta ho, unhe dard nahi dena chahta. Karan chahe jo bhi ho.

Lekin wohi aadmi, murgiyon ke dard ko nahi samajhna chahta. Karan chahe jo bhi ho.

Waise hamare liye yeh koi Naya anubhav nahi thaa. Saal pehle bhi yehi baat saamne aayi thee - https://youtu.be/edtH4SCJ7Wc
